  <h2>Before the Truck Arrives</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Clear access.</strong> Make a path a truck can use — mind gates, mud and low branches.</li>
    <li><strong>Expose the lids.</strong> Accessible lids avoid a digging step.</li>
    <li><strong>Know the distances.</strong> Hose length is limited; note where the tank sits relative to truck access.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>If You're Not Sure Where the Tank Is</h2>
  <p>
    If the tank location is unknown, a provider can locate it — see <a href="/septic-tank-locating-cookeville-tn/">tank locating</a>. When ready, <a href="/request-service/">request septic service</a>.
  </p>

